sub_title: Marketing, Public Relations & Communication at Neterra | Communication enthusiast | Telecommunications | Woman in tech | Writer | Passionate about content creation | Volunteer
summary:
Media and Communication graduate, eager to dive deeper in the broad world of Marketing, Communication and PR. 

Currently working as a Marketing & Public Relations Specialist at Neterra, a global connectivity and telecom solution provider,  trusted by some of the world's largest companies, as well as small and medium-sized businesses and providing international connectivity, network management services, and security for nearly 30 years across its core network of over 200 locations in 65+ countries.

A person constantly seeking for ways to improve both on personal and professional level. Passionate for creating content, PR and advertising but also having experience in digital marketing, research, customer behaviour and project management.

Looking forward to new opportunities, great experiences, broadening my knowledge and establishing new relationships in the Communication and Telecom world.
